          "type": "data",
          "data": {
            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h1 id=\"day-14-breaking-changes-elite-operations\">Day 14 \u2014 Breaking Changes &amp; Elite Operations</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<span class=\"paragraph\"><strong>WAF Pillars:</strong> Reliability \u00b7 Operational Excellence \u00b7 Security \u00b7 Performance\n<strong>Estimated time:</strong> 4 hours\n<strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Days 11-13 complete, all prior gate artifacts present\n<strong>Gates validated:</strong> ALL 17 (Gates 1-6 from <code>gates.py</code> + Gates 7-17 from <code>gates_v2.py</code>)</span>\n</blockquote>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"learning-objectives\">Learning Objectives</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Execute 10 failure-mode drills and record remediation steps.</li>\n<li>Perform a canary deployment with traffic splitting (10 % \u2192 100 %) and\n   automated rollback on regression.</li>\n<li>Verify data residency constraints using the ARM API (not string matching).</li>\n<li>Generate a CTO trace report aggregating all 17 gate results.</li>\n<li>Pass all 17 gates \u2014 the \"elite ops\" graduation requirement.</li>\n</ol>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"arc-position\">Arc Position</h2>\n<div class=\"language-text codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code>Day 11 \u2500\u2500\u25ba Day 12 \u2500\u2500\u25ba Day 13 \u2500\u2500\u25ba[Day 14]\nOBO        VNET       Integration  Elite Ops\n                      &amp; MCP        \u2190 ALL GATES HERE\n</code></pre></div>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">This is the final day.  Every artifact and gate from the full 14-day curriculum\nconverges here into one CTO-level trace report.</span></span>"
          }
        }
      ],
